author: M.H., Massachusetts
title: M.H., Massachusetts
text: I was a little skeptical at first, thinking this might be a site where you have to start selling your old stuff to get things you want. Turns out, no strings attatched, just good ol' quality, new or gently used products. Thank you. I will be browsing here first before I waste time searching the Internet. Bravo Couture Boutique!!
